					<div class="aefis-formitem" data-aefis-formitem-id="8533" data-aefis-formitem-code="TEXT" data-aefis-history-id="335200" style="visibility: hidden;background-color: transparent;color: #333333;text-decoration: none;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact">
									<div class="aefis-formItem-name-container row-fluid" style="visibility: hidden;background-color: transparent;color: #333333;text-decoration: none;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact;width: 100%;*zoom: 1;margin-bottom: 10px;font-size: 1.3em;font-weight: 400 !important">
										<h3 style="visibility: hidden;background-color: transparent;color: inherit;text-decoration: none;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;padding: 0 !important;margin: 0 !important;font-size: 1.17em;line-height: 1.2em !important;font-family: &quot;DM Sans&quot;, sans-serif !important;font-weight: 400 !important;text-rendering: optimizelegibility;-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact">Communication Policy:&nbsp;</h3>
									</div>
							<div class="aefis-formItem-options-container" style="visibility: hidden;background-color: transparent;color: #333333;text-decoration: none;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact;margin: 0px !important;font-size: 1.0em">
						<div class="aefis-formitem-options-container" style="visibility: hidden;background-color: transparent;color: #333333;text-decoration: none;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact;white-space: normal" data-aefis-enable-multiple-entires="false" data-aefis-empty-textarea="<div class=&quot;span11&quot;><textarea id=&quot;idhere&quot; name=&quot;idhere&quot; class=&quot;span11 editor&quot; data-aefis-formitem-option-id=&quot;8694&quot;></textarea></div>">
								<div class="form-item-option-text--response-container " style="visibility: hidden;background-color: transparent;color: #333333;text-decoration: none;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact">
									<p style="visibility: hidden;background-color: transparent;color: #333333;text-decoration: none;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact;padding: 0;font-weight: 400;line-height: inherit;font-size: inherit;letter-spacing: 0;margin: 0 0 10px;padding-bottom: 0em;padding-top: 0em"></p><p style="visibility: hidden;background-color: transparent;color: #333333;text-decoration: none;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact;padding: 0;font-weight: 400;line-height: inherit;font-size: inherit;letter-spacing: 0;margin: 0 0 10px;padding-bottom: 0em;padding-top: 0em">Use my email or Canvas Inbox for all email correspondence.&nbsp; Please be sure to include the course number in the subject line.</p><p style="visibility: hidden;background-color: transparent;color: #333333;text-decoration: none;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact;padding: 0;font-weight: 400;line-height: inherit;font-size: inherit;letter-spacing: 0;margin: 0 0 10px;padding-bottom: 0em;padding-top: 0em">I will typically respond to emails within 48 hours or earlier. If an issue is urgent, you are to indicate its urgency in the subject line and I will respond as soon as I am available to respond.</p><p style="visibility: hidden;background-color: transparent;color: #333333;text-decoration: none;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact;padding: 0;font-weight: 400;line-height: inherit;font-size: inherit;letter-spacing: 0;margin: 0 0 10px;padding-bottom: 0em;padding-top: 0em">
								</p></div>
						</div>
							</div>
					</div>
																</div>
