															<div class="syllabus-formItem-content-container" style="visibility: hidden;background-color: transparent;color: #333333;text-decoration: none;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact;margin-bottom: 15px">
																<div class="row-fluid" style="visibility: hidden;background-color: transparent;color: #333333;text-decoration: none;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact;width: 100%;*zoom: 1">
					<div class="aefis-formitem" data-aefis-formitem-id="8534" data-aefis-formitem-code="TEXT" data-aefis-history-id="69817" style="visibility: hidden;background-color: transparent;color: #333333;text-decoration: none;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact">
									<div class="aefis-formItem-name-container row-fluid" style="visibility: hidden;background-color: transparent;color: #333333;text-decoration: none;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact;width: 100%;*zoom: 1;margin-bottom: 10px;font-size: 1.3em;font-weight: 400 !important">
										<h3 style="visibility: hidden;background-color: transparent;color: inherit;text-decoration: none;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;padding: 0 !important;margin: 0 !important;font-size: 1.17em;line-height: 1.2em !important;font-family: &quot;DM Sans&quot;, sans-serif !important;font-weight: 400 !important;text-rendering: optimizelegibility;-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact">Office Hours:&nbsp;</h3>
									</div>
							<div class="aefis-formItem-options-container" style="visibility: hidden;background-color: transparent;color: #333333;text-decoration: none;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact;margin: 0px !important;font-size: 1.0em">
						<div class="aefis-formitem-options-container" style="visibility: hidden;background-color: transparent;color: #333333;text-decoration: none;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact;white-space: normal" data-aefis-enable-multiple-entires="false" data-aefis-empty-textarea="<div class=&quot;span11&quot;><textarea id=&quot;idhere&quot; name=&quot;idhere&quot; class=&quot;span11 editor&quot; data-aefis-formitem-option-id=&quot;8695&quot;></textarea></div>">
								<div class="form-item-option-text--response-container " style="visibility: hidden;background-color: transparent;color: #333333;text-decoration: none;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact">
									<p style="visibility: hidden;background-color: transparent;color: #333333;text-decoration: none;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact;padding: 0;font-weight: 400;line-height: inherit;font-size: inherit;letter-spacing: 0;margin: 0 0 10px;padding-bottom: 0em;padding-top: 0em"></p><p style="visibility: hidden;background-color: transparent;color: #333333;text-decoration: none;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact;padding: 0;font-weight: 400;line-height: inherit;font-size: inherit;letter-spacing: 0;margin: 0 0 10px;padding-bottom: 0em;padding-top: 0em">This course will use Zoom to facilitate weekly, synchronous office hours. You are not required to participate in office hours; however, you may find them very beneficial for receiving more timely answers to questions related to the course content and assignments.</p><p style="visibility: hidden;background-color: transparent;color: #333333;text-decoration: none;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact;padding: 0;font-weight: 400;line-height: inherit;font-size: inherit;letter-spacing: 0;margin: 0 0 10px;padding-bottom: 0em;padding-top: 0em">Office hours are scheduled through email with the instructor.&nbsp;&nbsp;I am generally available from around 6-8pm Wednesday and Thursday though other times can be arranged.&nbsp; Please email me with your availability and we can confirm a timeslot.<br style="visibility: hidden;background-color: transparent;color: #333333;text-decoration: none;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact"><br style="visibility: hidden;background-color: transparent;color: #333333;text-decoration: none;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact"><em style="visibility: hidden;background-color: transparent;color: #333333;text-decoration: none;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;font-style: italic;-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact">For more information regarding Zoom, please see the&nbsp;<a title="Zoom Student Quick Start Guide" href="https://jhubluejays.zoom.us/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" data-mce-href="https://jhubluejays.zoom.us/" style="visibility: hidden;background-color: transparent;color: #0077b3;text-decoration: none;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0);-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact;font-weight: inherit">Zoom Student Quick Start Guide</a>.</em><br style="visibility: hidden;background-color: transparent;color: #333333;text-decoration: none;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact"></p><p style="visibility: hidden;background-color: transparent;color: #333333;text-decoration: none;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact;padding: 0;font-weight: 400;line-height: inherit;font-size: inherit;letter-spacing: 0;margin: 0 0 10px;padding-bottom: 0em;padding-top: 0em">
								</p></div>
						</div>
							</div>
					</div>
																</div>
															</div>
														</div>
