								<div class="form-item-option-text--response-container " style="visibility: hidden;background-color: transparent;color: #333333;text-decoration: none;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact">
									<p style="visibility: hidden;background-color: transparent;color: #333333;text-decoration: none;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact;padding: 0;font-weight: 400;line-height: inherit;font-size: inherit;letter-spacing: 0;margin: 0 0 10px;padding-bottom: 0em;padding-top: 0em"></p><h2 style="visibility: hidden;background-color: transparent;color: inherit;text-decoration: none;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;padding: 0;font-family: &quot;DM Sans&quot;, sans-serif !important;font-weight: bold;font-size: 31.5px;line-height: 40px;margin: 10px 0;text-rendering: optimizelegibility;-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact">Required Hardware</h2><p style="visibility: hidden;background-color: transparent;color: #333333;text-decoration: none;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact;padding: 0;font-weight: 400;line-height: inherit;font-size: inherit;letter-spacing: 0;margin: 0 0 10px;padding-bottom: 0em;padding-top: 0em">Each registered student will be assigned an FPGA development board at the beginning of the semester. Each student is responsible for getting access to a VGA monitor with VGA cable and an oscilloscope for some of the labs.</p><p style="visibility: hidden;background-color: transparent;color: #333333;text-decoration: none;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact;padding: 0;font-weight: 400;line-height: inherit;font-size: inherit;letter-spacing: 0;margin: 0 0 10px;padding-bottom: 0em;padding-top: 0em"><strong style="visibility: hidden;background-color: transparent;color: #333333;text-decoration: none;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;font-weight: bold;-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact">Note:</strong> If you are registered for the course and receive a development board, you are expected to <strong style="visibility: hidden;background-color: transparent;color: #333333;text-decoration: none;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;font-weight: bold;-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact">return the development board to the EP program</strong>, when the course completes for the semester or when the student leaves the course.</p><p style="visibility: hidden;background-color: transparent;color: #333333;text-decoration: none;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact;padding: 0;font-weight: 400;line-height: inherit;font-size: inherit;letter-spacing: 0;margin: 0 0 10px;padding-bottom: 0em;padding-top: 0em">
								</p></div>
						</div>
							</div>
					</div>
																</div>
															</div>
														</div>
														<div class="row-fluid" style="visibility: hidden;background-color: transparent;color: #333333;text-decoration: none;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact;width: 100%;*zoom: 1">
															<div class="syllabus-formItem-content-container" style="visibility: hidden;background-color: transparent;color: #333333;text-decoration: none;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact;margin-bottom: 15px">
																<div class="row-fluid" style="visibility: hidden;background-color: transparent;color: #333333;text-decoration: none;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact;width: 100%;*zoom: 1">
					<div class="aefis-formitem" data-aefis-formitem-id="8542" data-aefis-formitem-code="TEXT" data-aefis-history-id="21315" style="visibility: hidden;background-color: transparent;color: #333333;text-decoration: none;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact">
									<div class="aefis-formItem-name-container row-fluid" style="visibility: hidden;background-color: transparent;color: #333333;text-decoration: none;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact;width: 100%;*zoom: 1;margin-bottom: 10px;font-size: 1.3em;font-weight: 400 !important">
										<h3 style="visibility: hidden;background-color: transparent;color: inherit;text-decoration: none;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;padding: 0 !important;margin: 0 !important;font-size: 1.17em;line-height: 1.2em !important;font-family: &quot;DM Sans&quot;, sans-serif !important;font-weight: 400 !important;text-rendering: optimizelegibility;-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact">Required Software:&nbsp;</h3>
									</div>
							<div class="aefis-formItem-options-container" style="visibility: hidden;background-color: transparent;color: #333333;text-decoration: none;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact;margin: 0px !important;font-size: 1.0em">
						<div class="aefis-formitem-options-container" style="visibility: hidden;background-color: transparent;color: #333333;text-decoration: none;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact;white-space: normal" data-aefis-enable-multiple-entires="false" data-aefis-empty-textarea="<div class=&quot;span11&quot;><textarea id=&quot;idhere&quot; name=&quot;idhere&quot; class=&quot;span11 editor&quot; data-aefis-formitem-option-id=&quot;8703&quot;></textarea></div>">
								<div class="form-item-option-text--response-container " style="visibility: hidden;background-color: transparent;color: #333333;text-decoration: none;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact">
									<p style="visibility: hidden;background-color: transparent;color: #333333;text-decoration: none;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact;padding: 0;font-weight: 400;line-height: inherit;font-size: inherit;letter-spacing: 0;margin: 0 0 10px;padding-bottom: 0em;padding-top: 0em"> <strong style="visibility: hidden;background-color: transparent;color: #333333;text-decoration: none;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;font-weight: bold;-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact">Xilinx Vivado</strong></p><p style="visibility: hidden;background-color: transparent;color: #333333;text-decoration: none;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact;padding: 0;font-weight: 400;line-height: inherit;font-size: inherit;letter-spacing: 0;margin: 0 0 10px;padding-bottom: 0em;padding-top: 0em">You will need access to a recent version of <strong style="visibility: hidden;background-color: transparent;color: #333333;text-decoration: none;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;font-weight: bold;-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact">Xilinx Vivdao</strong> 2020.1 or newer (<strong style="visibility: hidden;background-color: transparent;color: #333333;text-decoration: none;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;font-weight: bold;-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact">DO NOT install ISE</strong>). You can download the Xilinx Vivado webpack from: http://www.xilinx.com/support/download.html<br style="visibility: hidden;background-color: transparent;color: #333333;text-decoration: none;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact"></p><strong style="visibility: hidden;background-color: transparent;color: #333333;text-decoration: none;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;font-weight: bold;-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact">Digilent Nexys-4 Board Files</strong><p style="visibility: hidden;background-color: transparent;color: #333333;text-decoration: none;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact;padding: 0;font-weight: 400;line-height: inherit;font-size: inherit;letter-spacing: 0;margin: 0 0 10px;padding-bottom: 0em;padding-top: 0em">I also recommend installing the Nexys-4 Board files, which can be found here: https://github.com/Digilent/vivado-boards/archive/master.zip</p><p style="visibility: hidden;background-color: transparent;color: #333333;text-decoration: none;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact;padding: 0;font-weight: 400;line-height: inherit;font-size: inherit;letter-spacing: 0;margin: 0 0 10px;padding-bottom: 0em;padding-top: 0em">
								</p></div>
						</div>
							</div>
					</div>
																</div>
															</div>
														</div>
														<div class="row-fluid" style="visibility: hidden;background-color: transparent;color: #333333;text-decoration: none;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact;width: 100%;*zoom: 1">
															<div class="syllabus-formItem-content-container" style="visibility: hidden;background-color: transparent;color: #333333;text-decoration: none;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact;margin-bottom: 15px">
																<div class="row-fluid" style="visibility: hidden;background-color: transparent;color: #333333;text-decoration: none;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact;width: 100%;*zoom: 1">
					<div class="aefis-formitem" data-aefis-formitem-id="8543" data-aefis-formitem-code="HTML" data-aefis-history-id="0" style="visibility: hidden;background-color: transparent;color: #333333;text-decoration: none;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact">
									<div class="aefis-formItem-name-container row-fluid" style="visibility: hidden;background-color: transparent;color: #333333;text-decoration: none;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact;width: 100%;*zoom: 1;margin-bottom: 10px;font-size: 1.3em;font-weight: 400 !important">
										<h3 style="visibility: hidden;background-color: transparent;color: inherit;text-decoration: none;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;padding: 0 !important;margin: 0 !important;font-size: 1.17em;line-height: 1.2em !important;font-family: &quot;DM Sans&quot;, sans-serif !important;font-weight: 400 !important;text-rendering: optimizelegibility;-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact">Technical Requirements:&nbsp;</h3>
									</div>
							<div class="aefis-formItem-options-container" style="visibility: hidden;background-color: transparent;color: #333333;text-decoration: none;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact;margin: 0px !important;font-size: 1.0em">
				<div class="aefis-formitem-options-container" style="visibility: hidden;background-color: transparent;color: #333333;text-decoration: none;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact">
						You should refer to <a title="General Technical Requirements" href="https://ep.jhu.edu/faculty-staff/teaching-technology-resources/general-technical-requirements/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="visibility: hidden;background-color: transparent;color: #0077b3;text-decoration: none;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0);-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact;font-weight: inherit">General Technical Requirements</a> for guidance on system requirements. Access support resources from the <strong style="visibility: hidden;background-color: transparent;color: #333333;text-decoration: none;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;font-weight: bold;-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact">Help</strong> menu if you encounter any technical issues.
				</div>
							</div>
