ed office&nbsp;</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW65554401 BCX0" data-ccp-parastyle="JHEP Body" style="visibility: hidden;background-color: transparent;color: #333333;text-decoration: none;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact">for&nbsp;</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW65554401 BCX0" data-ccp-parastyle="JHEP Body" style="visibility: hidden;background-color: transparent;color: #333333;text-decoration: none;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact">Student Support and Advocacy. </span></span><a class="Hyperlink SCXW65554401 BCX0" href="https://engineering.jhu.edu/studentaffairs/navigatingnonacademicissues/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="visibility: hidden;background-color: transparent;color: #0077b3;text-decoration: none;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0);-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact;font-weight: inherit"><span class="TextRun Highlight Underlined SCXW65554401 BCX0" lang="EN-US" xml:lang="EN-US" data-contrast="none" style="visibility: hidden;background-color: transparent;color: #333333;text-decoration: none;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact"><span class="NormalTextRun CommentStart SCXW65554401 BCX0" data-ccp-charstyle="Hyperlink" style="visibility: hidden;background-color: transparent;color: #333333;text-decoration: none;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact">Engineering Student Support &amp; Advocacy (ESSA)</span></span></a><span class="TextRun Highlight SCXW65554401 BCX0" lang="EN-US" xml:lang="EN-US" data-contrast="auto" style="visibility: hidden;background-color: transparent;color: #333333;text-decoration: none;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW65554401 BCX0" data-ccp-parastyle="JHEP Body" style="visibility: hidden;background-color: transparent;color: #333333;text-decoration: none;-webkit-tap-highli