ackground-color: transparent;color: #333333;text-decoration: none;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact">TimelyCare</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW92493013 BCX0" data-ccp-parastyle="JHEP Body" style="visibility: hidden;background-color: transparent;color: #333333;text-decoration: none;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact">&nbsp;for routine medication management (no stimulants or other controlled substances). </span></span><span class="EOP SCXW92493013 BCX0" data-ccp-props="{&quot;335559738&quot;:240,&quot;335559739&quot;:240}" style="visibility: hidden;background-color: transparent;color: #333333;text-decoration: none;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact">&nbsp;</span></p>
