												<div style="visibility: hidden;background-color: transparent;color: #333333;text-decoration: none;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact">
													<h3 class="aefis--h3" style="visibility: hidden;background-color: transparent;color: inherit;text-decoration: none;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;padding: 0;margin: 10px 0;font-size: 1.3em;line-height: 40px;font-family: &quot;DM Sans&quot;, sans-serif !important;font-weight: 500;text-rendering: optimizelegibility;-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact">
														Deadlines for Adding, Dropping, and Withdrawing from Courses 
													</h3>
													<p class="aefis-syllabus-text" style="visibility: hidden;background-color: transparent;color: #444;text-decoration: none;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact;padding: 0;font-weight: 400;line-height: inherit;font-size: 14px;letter-spacing: 0;margin: 0 0 10px;padding-bottom: 0em;padding-top: 0em">
														</p><p style="visibility: hidden;background-color: transparent;color: #333333;text-decoration: none;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact;padding: 0;font-weight: 400;line-height: inherit;font-size: inherit;letter-spacing: 0;margin: 0 0 10px;padding-bottom: 0em;padding-top: 0em"><span lang="EN-US" xml:lang="EN-US" data-contrast="auto" style="visibility: hidden;background-color: transparent;color: #333333;text-decoration: none;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact">Students may add a course up to one week after the start of the term for that particular course.&nbsp;Students may drop courses according to the drop deadlines outlined in the&nbsp;</span><a href="https://ep.jhu.edu/student-services/academic-calendar/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="visibility: hidden;background-color: transparent;color: #0077b3;text-decoration: none;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0);-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact;font-weight: inherit"><span lang="EN-US" xml:lang="EN-US" data-contrast="none" style="visibility: hidden;background-color: transparent;color: #333333;text-decoration: none;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact">EP academic calendar</span></a><span lang="EN-US" xml:lang="EN-US" data-contrast="auto" style="visibility: hidden;background-color: transparent;color: #333333;text-decoration: none;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact">. Between the 6th week of the class and prior to the final withdrawal deadline, a student may withdraw from a course with a W on their academic record. A record of the course will remain on the academic record with a W appearing in the grade column to&nbsp;indicate&nbsp;that the student registered and withdrew from the course.</span>&nbsp;</p>
													<p style="visibility: hidden;background-color: transparent;color: #333333;text-decoration: none;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact;padding: 0;font-weight: 400;line-height: inherit;font-size: inherit;letter-spacing: 0;margin: 0 0 10px;padding-bottom: 0em;padding-top: 0em">
												</p></div>
										</div>
									</li>
									<li style="visibility: hidden;background-color: transparent;color: #333333;text-decoration: none;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact">
										<div style="visibility: hidden;background-color: transparent;color: #333333;text-decoration: none;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact;display: inline-flex;align-items: top">
												<div style="visibility: hidden;background-color: transparent;color: #333333;text-decoration: none;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact;width: 45px;padding: 10px 5px 10px 0px">
													<div aria-hidden="true" class="circle medium mdl-color--deep-purple mdl-color-text--white" style="visibility: hidden;background-color: #673ab7 !important;color: #fff !important;text-decoration: none;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact;border-radius: 50%;text-align: center;display: inline-block;position: relative;width: 38px;height: 38px;font-size: 1.3em;line-height: 48px;background: #ddd">
														<div class="circle--inner" style="visibility: hidden;background-color: transparent;color: #ffffff;text-decoration: none;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact;width: 36px;height: 36px;position: absolute;margin: auto;top: 0;right: 0;bottom: 0;left: 0">
															<i style="visibility: hidden;background-color: transparent;color: #333333;text-decoration: none;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact"></i>
														</div>
													</div>
												</div>
												<div style="visibility: hidden;background-color: transparent;color: #333333;text-decoration: none;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact">
													<h3 class="aefis--h3" style="visibility: hidden;background-color: transparent;color: inherit;text-decoration: none;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;padding: 0;margin: 10px 0;font-size: 1.3em;line-height: 40px;font-family: &quot;DM Sans&quot;, sans-serif !important;font-weight: 500;text-rendering: optimizelegibility;-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact">
														Academic Misconduct Policy
													</h3>
													<p class="aefis-syllabus-text" style="visibility: hidden;background-color: transparent;color: #444;text-decoration: none;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact;padding: 0;font-weight: 400;line-height: inherit;font-size: 14px;letter-spacing: 0;margin: 0 0 10px;padding-bottom: 0em;padding-top: 0em">
														</p><div style="visibility: hidden;background-color: transparent;color: #333333;text-decoration: none;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact">
<p style="visibility: hidden;background-color: transparent;color: #333333;text-decoration: none;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact;padding: 0;font-weight: 400;line-height: inherit;font-size: inherit;letter-spacing: 0;margin: 0 0 10px;padding-bottom: 0em;padding-top: 0em"><span lang="EN-US" xml:lang="EN-US" data-contrast="auto" style="visibility: hidden;background-color: transparent;color: #333333;text-decoration: none;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact">All students&nbsp;are required to&nbsp;read, know, and&nbsp;comply with&nbsp;the Johns Hopkins University Krieger School of Arts and Sciences (KSAS) / Whiting School of Engineering (WSE) </span><a href="https://ep.jhu.edu/wseacademicmisconductpolicy" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="visibility: hidden;background-color: transparent;color: #0077b3;text-decoration: none;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0);-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact;font-weight: inherit"><span lang="EN-US" xml:lang="EN-US" data-contrast="none" style="visibility: hidden;background-color: transparent;color: #333333;text-decoration: none;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact">Procedures for Handling Allegations of Misconduct</span></a><span lang="EN-US" xml:lang="EN-US" data-contrast="auto" style="visibility: hidden;background-color: transparent;color: #333333;text-decoration: none;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact"> by Full-Time and Part-Time Graduate Students.</span></p>
</div>
<div style="visibility: hidden;background-color: transparent;color: #333333;text-decoration: none;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact">
<p style="visibility: hidden;background-color: transparent;color: #333333;text-decoration: none;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact;padding: 0;font-weight: 400;line-height: inherit;font-size: inherit;letter-spacing: 0;margin: 0 0 10px;padding-bottom: 0em;padding-top: 0em"><span lang="EN-US" xml:lang="EN-US" data-contrast="auto" style="visibility: hidden;background-color: transparent;color: #333333;text-decoration: none;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact">This policy prohibits academic misconduct, including but not limited to the following: cheating or&nbsp;facilitating&nbsp;cheating; plagiarism; reuse of assignments; unauthorized collaboration; alteration of graded assignments; and unfair competition. Course materials (old assignments, texts, or examinations, etc.) should not be shared unless authorized by the course instructor. Any questions related to this policy should be directed to&nbsp;EP's&nbsp;academic integrity officer at </span><a href="mailto:ep-academic-integrity@jhu.edu" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="visibility: hidden;background-color: transparent;color: #0077b3;text-decoration: none;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0);-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact;font-weight: inherit"><span lang="EN-US" xml:lang="EN-US" data-contrast="none" style="visibility: hidden;background-color: transparent;color: #333333;text-decoration: none;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact">ep-academic-integrity@jhu.edu</span></a><span lang="EN-US" xml:lang="EN-US" data-contrast="auto" style="visibility: hidden;background-color: transparent;color: #333333;text-decoration: none;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact">.</span></p>
</div>
													<p style="visibility: hidden;background-color: transparent;color: #333333;text-decoration: none;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact;padding: 0;font-weight: 400;line-height: inherit;font-size: inherit;letter-spacing: 0;margin: 0 0 10px;padding-bottom: 0em;padding-top: 0em">
												</p></div>
										</div>
									</li>
									<li style="visibility: hidden;background-color: transparent;color: #333333;text-decoration: none;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact">
										<div style="visibility: hidden;background-color: transparent;color: #333333;text-decoration: none;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact;display: inline-flex;align-items: top">
												<div style="visibility: hidden;background-color: transparent;color: #333333;text-decoration: none;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact;width: 45px;padding: 10px 5px 10px 0px">
													<div aria-hidden="true" class="circle medium mdl-color--deep-purple mdl-color-text--white" style="visibility: hidden;background-color: #673ab7 !important;color: #fff !important;text-decoration: none;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact;border-radius: 50%;text-align: center;display: inline-block;position: relative;width: 38px;height: 38px;font-size: 1.3em;line-height: 48px;background: #ddd">
														<div class="circle--inner" style="visibility: hidden;background-color: transparent;color: #ffffff;text-decoration: none;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact;width: 36px;height: 36px;position: absolute;margin: auto;top: 0;right: 0;bottom: 0;left: 0">
															<i style="visibility: hidden;background-color: transparent;color: #333333;text-decoration: none;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact"></i>
														</div>
													</div>
												</div>
												<div style="visibility: hidden;background-color: transparent;color: #333333;text-decoration: none;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact">
													<h3 class="aefis--h3" style="visibility: hidden;background-color: transparent;color: inherit;text-decoration: none;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;padding: 0;margin: 10px 0;font-size: 1.3em;line-height: 40px;font-family: &quot;DM Sans&quot;, sans-serif !important;font-weight: 500;text-rendering: optimizelegibility;-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact">
														Students with Disabilities - Accommodations and Accessibility
													</h3>
													<p class="aefis-syllabus-text" style="visibility: hidden;background-color: transparent;color: #444;text-decoration: none;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact;padding: 0;font-weight: 400;line-height: inherit;font-size: 14px;letter-spacing: 0;margin: 0 0 10px;padding-bottom: 0em;padding-top: 0em">
														</p><div style="visibility: hidden;background-color: transparent;color: #333333;text-decoration: none;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact">
<p style="visibility: hidden;background-color: transparent;color: #333333;text-decoration: none;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact;padding: 0;font-weight: 400;line-height: inherit;font-size: inherit;letter-spacing: 0;margin: 0 0 10px;padding-bottom: 0em;padding-top: 0em"><span lang="EN-US" xml:lang="EN-US" data-contrast="auto" style="visibility: hidden;background-color: transparent;color: #333333;text-decoration: none;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact">Johns Hopkins University values diversity and inclusion. We are committed to providing welcoming,&nbsp;equitable, and accessible educational experiences for all students.&nbsp;</span><span lang="EN-US" xml:lang="EN-US" data-contrast="none" style="visibility: hidden;background-color: transparent;color: #333333;text-decoration: none;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact">Our courses&nbsp;are designed&nbsp;with&nbsp;a proactive approach to accessibility&nbsp;to minimize the need for disability disclosure and accommodation requests, but we recognize that you may need&nbsp;additional&nbsp;support.&nbsp;</span><span lang="EN-US" xml:lang="EN-US" data-contrast="auto" style="visibility: hidden;background-color: transparent;color: #333333;text-decoration: none;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact">Students with disabilities (including those with psychological conditions, medical conditions,&nbsp;and temporary disabilities) can request accommodations for this course by providing an Accommodation Letter issued by&nbsp;</span><a href="https://sds.jhu.edu/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="visibility: hidden;background-color: transparent;color: #0077b3;text-decoration: none;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0);-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact;font-weight: inherit"><span lang="EN-US" xml:lang="EN-US" data-contrast="none" style="visibility: hidden;background-color: transparent;color: #333333;text-decoration: none;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact">Student Disability Services (SDS)</span></a><span lang="EN-US" xml:lang="EN-US" data-contrast="auto" style="visibility: hidden;background-color: transparent;color: #333333;text-decoration: none;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact">. Please request&nbsp;accommodations&nbsp;for this course as early as possible to provide time for effective communication and arrangements.</span>&nbsp;</p>
</div>
<div style="visibility: hidden;background-color: transparent;color: #333333;text-decoration: none;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact">
