									<li style="visibility: hidden;background-color: transparent;color: #333333;text-decoration: none;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact">
										<div style="visibility: hidden;background-color: transparent;color: #333333;text-decoration: none;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact;display: inline-flex;align-items: top">
												<div style="visibility: hidden;background-color: transparent;color: #333333;text-decoration: none;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact;width: 45px;padding: 10px 5px 10px 0px">
													<div aria-hidden="true" class="circle medium mdl-color--deep-purple mdl-color-text--white" style="visibility: hidden;background-color: #673ab7 !important;color: #fff !important;text-decoration: none;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact;border-radius: 50%;text-align: center;display: inline-block;position: relative;width: 38px;height: 38px;font-size: 1.3em;line-height: 48px;background: #ddd">
														<div class="circle--inner" style="visibility: hidden;background-color: transparent;color: #ffffff;text-decoration: none;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact;width: 36px;height: 36px;position: absolute;margin: auto;top: 0;right: 0;bottom: 0;left: 0">
															<i style="visibility: hidden;background-color: transparent;color: #333333;text-decoration: none;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact"></i>
														</div>
													</div>
												</div>
												<div style="visibility: hidden;background-color: transparent;color: #333333;text-decoration: none;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact">
													<h3 class="aefis--h3" style="visibility: hidden;background-color: transparent;color: inherit;text-decoration: none;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;padding: 0;margin: 10px 0;font-size: 1.3em;line-height: 40px;font-family: &quot;DM Sans&quot;, sans-serif !important;font-weight: 500;text-rendering: optimizelegibility;-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact">
														Student Conduct Code
													</h3>
													<p class="aefis-syllabus-text" style="visibility: hidden;background-color: transparent;color: #444;text-decoration: none;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact;padding: 0;font-weight: 400;line-height: inherit;font-size: 14px;letter-spacing: 0;margin: 0 0 10px;padding-bottom: 0em;padding-top: 0em">
														</p><div style="visibility: hidden;background-color: transparent;color: #333333;text-decoration: none;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact">
<p style="visibility: hidden;background-color: transparent;color: #333333;text-decoration: none;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact;padding: 0;font-weight: 400;line-height: inherit;font-size: inherit;letter-spacing: 0;margin: 0 0 10px;padding-bottom: 0em;padding-top: 0em"><span lang="EN-US" xml:lang="EN-US" data-contrast="auto" style="visibility: hidden;background-color: transparent;color: #333333;text-decoration: none;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact">The fundamental purpose of the JHU regulation of student conduct is to promote and to protect the health, safety, welfare, property, and rights of all members of the University community as well as to promote the orderly operation of the University and to safeguard its property and facilities. As members of the University community, students accept certain responsibilities which support the educational mission and create an environment in which all students are afforded the same opportunity to succeed academically.</span></p>
</div>
<div style="visibility: hidden;background-color: transparent;color: #333333;text-decoration: none;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact">
<p style="visibility: hidden;background-color: transparent;color: #333333;text-decoration: none;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact;padding: 0;font-weight: 400;line-height: inherit;font-size: inherit;letter-spacing: 0;margin: 0 0 10px;padding-bottom: 0em;padding-top: 0em"><span lang="EN-US" xml:lang="EN-US" data-contrast="auto" style="visibility: hidden;background-color: transparent;color: #333333;text-decoration: none;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact">For a full description of the code please visit the&nbsp;</span><a href="https://studentaffairs.jhu.edu/policies-guidelines/student-code/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="visibility: hidden;background-color: transparent;color: #0077b3;text-decoration: none;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0);-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact;font-weight: inherit"><span lang="EN-US" xml:lang="EN-US" data-contrast="none" style="visibility: hidden;background-color: transparent;color: #333333;text-decoration: none;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact">Student Conduct Code website</span></a><span lang="EN-US" xml:lang="EN-US" data-contrast="auto" style="visibility: hidden;background-color: transparent;color: #333333;text-decoration: none;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact">.</span></p>
</div>
													<p style="visibility: hidden;background-color: transparent;color: #333333;text-decoration: none;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact;padding: 0;font-weight: 400;line-height: inherit;font-size: inherit;letter-spacing: 0;margin: 0 0 10px;padding-bottom: 0em;padding-top: 0em">
												</p></div>
										</div>
									</li>
									<li style="visibility: hidden;background-color: transparent;color: #333333;text-decoration: none;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact">
										<div style="visibility: hidden;background-color: transparent;color: #333333;text-decoration: none;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact;display: inline-flex;align-items: top">
												<div style="visibility: hidden;background-color: transparent;color: #333333;text-decoration: none;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact;width: 45px;padding: 10px 5px 10px 0px">
													<div aria-hidden="true" class="circle medium mdl-color--deep-purple mdl-color-text--white" style="visibility: hidden;background-color: #673ab7 !important;color: #fff !important;text-decoration: none;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact;border-radius: 50%;text-align: center;display: inline-block;position: relative;width: 38px;height: 38px;font-size: 1.3em;line-height: 48px;background: #ddd">
														<div class="circle--inner" style="visibility: hidden;background-color: transparent;color: #ffffff;text-decoration: none;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact;width: 36px;height: 36px;position: absolute;margin: auto;top: 0;right: 0;bottom: 0;left: 0">
															<i style="visibility: hidden;background-color: transparent;color: #333333;text-decoration: none;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact"></i>
														</div>
													</div>
												</div>
												<div style="visibility: hidden;background-color: transparent;color: #333333;text-decoration: none;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact">
													<h3 class="aefis--h3" style="visibility: hidden;background-color: transparent;color: inherit;text-decoration: none;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;padding: 0;margin: 10px 0;font-size: 1.3em;line-height: 40px;font-family: &quot;DM Sans&quot;, sans-serif !important;font-weight: 500;text-rendering: optimizelegibility;-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact">
														Classroom Climate
													</h3>
													<p class="aefis-syllabus-text" style="visibility: hidden;background-color: transparent;color: #444;text-decoration: none;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact;padding: 0;font-weight: 400;line-height: inherit;font-size: 14px;letter-spacing: 0;margin: 0 0 10px;padding-bottom: 0em;padding-top: 0em">
														</p><p style="visibility: hidden;background-color: transparent;color: #333333;text-decoration: none;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact;padding: 0;font-weight: 400;line-height: inherit;font-size: inherit;letter-spacing: 0;margin: 0 0 10px;padding-bottom: 0em;padding-top: 0em"><span lang="EN-US" xml:lang="EN-US" data-contrast="auto" style="visibility: hidden;background-color: transparent;color: #333333;text-decoration: none;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact">JHU is committed to creating a classroom environment that values the diversity of experiences and perspectives that all students bring. Everyone has the right to be treated with dignity and respect. Fostering an inclusive climate is important. Research and experience show that students who interact with peers who are different from themselves learn new things and experience tangible educational outcomes.&nbsp;At no time in this learning process should someone be singled out or treated unequally on the basis of any seen or unseen part of their identity.</span></p>
<p style="visibility: hidden;background-color: transparent;color: #333333;text-decoration: none;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact;padding: 0;font-weight: 400;line-height: inherit;font-size: inherit;letter-spacing: 0;margin: 0 0 10px;padding-bottom: 0em;padding-top: 0em"><span lang="EN-US" xml:lang="EN-US" data-contrast="auto" style="visibility: hidden;background-color: transparent;color: #333333;text-decoration: none;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact">If you have concerns in this course about harassment, discrimination, or any unequal treatment, or if you seek accommodations or resources, please reach out to the course instructor directly. Reporting will never impact&nbsp;your course grade. You may also share concerns with your program chair, the Assistant Dean for Diversity and Inclusion, or the </span><a href="https://oie.jhu.edu/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="visibility: hidden;background-color: transparent;color: #0077b3;text-decoration: none;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0);-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact;font-weight: inherit"><span lang="EN-US" xml:lang="EN-US" data-contrast="none" style="visibility: hidden;background-color: transparent;color: #333333;text-decoration: none;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact">Office of Institutional Equity</span></a><span lang="EN-US" xml:lang="EN-US" data-contrast="auto" style="visibility: hidden;background-color: transparent;color: #333333;text-decoration: none;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact">. In handling reports, people will protect your privacy as much as possible, but faculty and staff&nbsp;are required to&nbsp;officially report information for some cases (e.g.&nbsp;sexual harassment).</span></p>
													<p style="visibility: hidden;background-color: transparent;color: #333333;text-decoration: none;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact;padding: 0;font-weight: 400;line-height: inherit;font-size: inherit;letter-spacing: 0;margin: 0 0 10px;padding-bottom: 0em;padding-top: 0em">
												</p></div>
										</div>
									</li>
									<li style="visibility: hidden;background-color: transparent;color: #333333;text-decoration: none;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact">
										<div style="visibility: hidden;background-color: transparent;color: #333333;text-decoration: none;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact;display: inline-flex;align-items: top">
												<div style="visibility: hidden;background-color: transparent;color: #333333;text-decoration: none;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact;width: 45px;padding: 10px 5px 10px 0px">
													<div aria-hidden="true" class="circle medium mdl-color--deep-purple mdl-color-text--white" style="visibility: hidden;background-color: #673ab7 !important;color: #fff !important;text-decoration: none;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact;border-radius: 50%;text-align: center;display: inline-block;position: relative;width: 38px;height: 38px;font-size: 1.3em;line-height: 48px;background: #ddd">
														<div class="circle--inner" style="visibility: hidden;background-color: transparent;color: #ffffff;text-decoration: none;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact;width: 36px;height: 36px;position: absolute;margin: auto;top: 0;right: 0;bottom: 0;left: 0">
															<i style="visibility: hidden;background-color: transparent;color: #333333;text-decoration: none;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact"></i>
														</div>
													</div>
												</div>
												<div style="visibility: hidden;background-color: transparent;color: #333333;text-decoration: none;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact">
													<h3 class="aefis--h3" style="visibility: hidden;background-color: transparent;color: inherit;text-decoration: none;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;padding: 0;margin: 10px 0;font-size: 1.3em;line-height: 40px;font-family: &quot;DM Sans&quot;, sans-serif !important;font-weight: 500;text-rendering: optimizelegibility;-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact">
														Course Auditing
													</h3>
													<p class="aefis-syllabus-text" style="visibility: hidden;background-color: transparent;color: #444;text-decoration: none;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact;padding: 0;font-weight: 400;line-height: inherit;font-size: 14px;letter-spacing: 0;margin: 0 0 10px;padding-bottom: 0em;padding-top: 0em">
														</p><p style="visibility: hidden;background-color: transparent;color: #333333;text-decoration: none;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact;padding: 0;font-weight: 400;line-height: inherit;font-size: inherit;letter-spacing: 0;margin: 0 0 10px;padding-bottom: 0em;padding-top: 0em"><span lang="EN-US" xml:lang="EN-US" data-contrast="auto" style="visibility: hidden;background-color: transparent;color: #333333;text-decoration: none;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact">When a student enrolls in an EP course with "audit" status, the student must reach an understanding with the instructor as to what is&nbsp;required&nbsp;to earn the "audit." If the student does not meet those expectations, the instructor must notify the EP Registration Team&nbsp;(</span><a href="mailto:EP-Registration@exchange.johnshopkins.edu" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="visibility: hidden;background-color: transparent;color: #0077b3;text-decoration: none;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0);-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact;font-weight: inherit"><span lang="EN-US" xml:lang="EN-US" data-contrast="none" style="visibility: hidden;background-color: transparent;color: #333333;text-decoration: none;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact">EP-Registration@exchange.johnshopkins.edu</span></a><span lang="EN-US" xml:lang="EN-US" data-contrast="auto" style="visibility: hidden;background-color: transparent;color: #333333;text-decoration: none;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact">)&nbsp;in order for&nbsp;the student to be retroactively dropped or withdrawn from the course (depending on when the "audit" was requested and&nbsp;in accordance with&nbsp;EP registration deadlines). All lecture content will remain accessible to auditing students, but access to all other course&nbsp;material&nbsp;is left to the discretion of the instructor.</span></p>
<p style="visibility: hidden;background-color: transparent;color: #333333;text-decoration: none;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact;padding: 0;font-weight: 400;line-height: inherit;font-size: inherit;letter-spacing: 0;margin: 0 0 10px;padding-bottom: 0em;padding-top: 0em"><!-- [if gte mso 9]><xml>
